title: Ep 38 - Replace Worry With Action
itunes:title: Ep 38 - Replace Worry With Action
description:
Worrying does nothing for us. We will all worry, it is part of life, but the key is to not let that worry cripple us and to take action in order to overcome that worry. In this episode we talk about how to overcome our worrying and take action towards the outcome we desire.
